<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification - LeadClaim</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #FFF1F2;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 5px solid #B0153D;
      "
    >
      <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
        <img
          src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3176/3176363.png"
          alt="LeadClaim Logo"
          width="64"
          style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: 26px; color: #B0153D; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: 700;">
        Welcome to LeadClaim! ðŸš€
      </h1>
      
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555555; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        Manage your sales leads efficiently and close more deals.
      </p>

      <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;" />

      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 15px;">
        Hi {{name}},
      </h2>
      
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        Thank you for joining <strong>LeadClaim</strong>. To verify your account and start organizing your sales pipeline, please click the button below.
      </p>

      <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
        <a
          href="{{link}}"
          target="_blank"
          style="
            background-color: #B0153D;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(176, 21, 61, 0.3);
          "
        >
          Verify My Account
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #999999; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        This link will expire in 24 hours.
      </p>

      <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;" />

      <p
        style="
          font-size: 12px;
          color: #aaaaaa;
          line-height: 1.5;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
        "
      >
        If you didnâ€™t create an account on LeadClaim, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
      
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; margin: 0;">
        &copy; {{year}} LeadClaim System. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>